{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act25side", "eventName": "孤星", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CW-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "台前幕後", "storyInfo": "爾虞我詐之下，最終是梅蘭德的勝利。塵埃落定之時，塞雷婭、伊芙利特遇見了赫默。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g9_headquarter", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$skill_flash", "volume": 0.5, "channel": "x"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“科技是哥倫比亞的未來”並不是一句漂亮話或者廣告語，雅拉主任，我今天像是一個第一次上科學課的孩子，真是大開眼界。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜時間太短，還有好多感興趣的項目沒來得及聽你們講解。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵生命隨時歡迎您的再次到來，傑克遜先生。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝你，雅拉主任。今天太過興師動眾，希望沒有給你帶來不便。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您太客氣了，我今天只是您的導遊而已。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能讓曾經紅極一時的瑪麗安娜·布萊克女士充當導遊，是我特里蒙之行的又一大收穫。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不瞞您說，我也是您的粉絲。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#6$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我收藏了您出道作品的簽名海報，並把它貼在了我辦公室的牆壁上。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的嗎？", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#10$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實不相瞞，那正是我太太送我的就職禮物，哈哈。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕瓦爾，有關萊茵生命在特區新建研發基地的申請，或許可以關照一下特區政府的推進。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記下來了，先生。", "name": "副總統秘書"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，今天的行程就到這裡了，雅拉女士。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也祝您在特里蒙接下來的旅程順利。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#5$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好的祝福。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一天已經過去，希望接下來也都是晴天。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$skill_flash", "volume": 0.3, "channel": "x"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$skill_flash", "volume": 0.3, "channel": "y", "delay": 0.15}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快拍、快拍......", "name": "記者"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$skill_flash", "volume": 0.3, "channel": "y", "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "副總統先生，請問您如何評價這次的萊茵之旅？", "name": "記者"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位不要著急，副總統先生特意留出了十分鐘的時間接受採訪，請有序發言。", "name": "萊茵職員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "記者"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_strangeclap"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒有聽錯，我正在鼓掌。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“副總統與萊茵生命人力資源科主任相談甚歡”“副總統訪問助推萊茵生命的科技巨頭之路”，我都能猜到這幫記者會配什麼標題。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "活動已經結束，現場沒有異常情況，副總統將在十分鐘後離開萊茵生命。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......博士。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cherunder_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，已經收到了你傳過來的路線圖。", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說，還有一條可供潛入的秘密路線，直通地下結構，但不在繆爾賽思給你的圖紙上？", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "交給我好了！", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#2$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和迷迭香在上面跟動力甲打得熱火朝天，我在連接層蹲守了半天，別說可疑的人了，壓根就沒有人......", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#2$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞雷婭會來找我？", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#5$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我也得先前往地下結構，不是說副總統還有幾分鐘就要離開了嗎，得盡快排除風險才行。", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（壓低聲音）就這樣，伊芙利特開始行動，博士。", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我回來了。", "name": "特工A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上面怎麼樣了？", "name": "特工B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽不太清楚，我沒上到地面，但好像沒什麼特別的動靜。", "name": "特工A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我估計，沒得手。", "name": "特工A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們？", "name": "特工B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照上校的命令，開啟了訊號干擾，不支援任何其他單位......應該沒有人查到這裡來，斐爾迪南提供的潛入路徑很隱蔽。", "name": "特工A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行作戰計劃吧。對一下錶......嗯，也差不多到時間了。", "name": "特工A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炸藥怎麼樣了？", "name": "特工A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛剛去查探情況的時候已經佈置好了......兩管改造過的塑性炸藥，足夠破壞這層防洩漏裝置。", "name": "特工B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過斐爾迪南也真夠狠的，這可是他們能量科專用的液化源石氣管道，他不是還說要回萊茵生命嗎？", "name": "特工B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按上校的說法，他和咱們現在是拴在一條線上的蟲子，沒得選擇。", "name": "特工A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我不明白現在搞這麼一場爆破的意義在哪裡......", "name": "特工B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "副總統這個時間點應該已經離開萊茵生命了，大樓地下結構的液化源石氣管道爆炸，能傷得到他嗎？", "name": "特工B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上校自有他的安排，執行命令就好了。", "name": "特工A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_imp_rockthrow"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sandstone"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼人？", "name": "特工A"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個......孩子？", "name": "特工B"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士的情報真準，還真有人......", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你們兩個，雖然不知道你們躲在這裡想幹什麼，但是可以投降了。", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g11_monitoringroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_bat_imprisonment_intro", "key": "$m_bat_imprisonment_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有作戰單位全部失去聯絡？", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#6$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是的，都是通訊突然中斷。", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從現場的情況來看，副總統及隨行人員、記者......沒有人有特別的反應，看來我們派出的人在行動之前就已經被按下了。", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我們在萊茵內部的行動也出現了混亂，據說受到了一批動力甲的干擾。", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哼。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能夠監視各個路口的攝影機訊號也在陸續被掐斷。", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上校，我們正在失去對現場的掌控。", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能我們佈置得天衣無縫的計劃，在梅蘭德基金會構建的情報網裡，根本就是漏洞百出。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這起刺殺計劃本來就很倉促，他們做出了應對也很正常。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上校，那......我們要撤離嗎？", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然對方的反應這麼快，遲早會查到這裡來。", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不急......", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得副總統先生說過，他希望“和優秀的科研人員好好交流”，我本來也打算滿足他這個願望。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "C1、C2那邊有什麼反應？", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "訊號穩定，還在指定位置。", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷克，控制台右上角的那個遙控裝置，啟動它。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布萊克所說的遙控裝置，只是一枚看起來相當普通的機械按鈕，還採用了老式的安全閥鎖定裝置。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "士兵輸入密碼，透明的安全閥應聲彈開，紅色的按鈕暴露在空氣中。"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上校，這是？", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工程炸藥的遙控裝置，用來炸毀液化源石氣管道的阻斷結構。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......！", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看螢幕，對，根據斐爾迪南提供的入侵路線，在萊茵生命大樓的西側，有幾條專供能量科的液化源石氣管道。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵生命工程科的工作做得很細緻......", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#4$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了防護裝置，還在一定範圍內增設了地下阻斷結構，應用的特殊材料能夠防止洩露的液化源石氣引發連環爆炸。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#4$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本的計劃，是透過爆破，造成液化源石氣洩露，引發騷亂，為地面上的人創造接近傑克遜的機會。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#4$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但巧合的是，傑克遜車隊預定的回程路線，正好和液化源石氣管道有一處交會。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#4$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cherunder_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是......萊茵生命的員工？", "name": "特工A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看著倒是一副不好惹的樣子......聽說防衛科裡有不少脾氣很衝的傢伙，但也不應該雇傭這麼小的孩子。", "name": "特工A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說了讓你們投降，怎麼話那麼多？", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會盡量控制一下，不把你們兩個烤成焦炭，畢竟說不定博士和塞雷婭想要親自審審你們這些壞人，讓你們當證人什麼的。", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，你手裡拿的是......噴火器？", "name": "特工B"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這周圍可都是液化源石氣管道，小心！", "name": "特工B"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "伊芙利特"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來你們是想......", "name": "伊芙利特"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.55", "scale": 1.1, "duration": 0.2, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_fastener"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "delay": 0.5, "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火紅的薩弗拉孩子在一秒鐘之內完成了判斷，她扣上火焰放射器的安全鎖，抬手用力砸向左邊的人。"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下一秒，她全力向右邊衝出，一拳揮中右邊人的臉頰。"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像是火焰即明即滅，伊芙利特已經重新站穩，並俐落地拍了拍手掌。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咕......", "name": "特工A"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的鼻樑大概斷了......", "name": "特工B"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，你快跑吧......", "name": "特工B"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔？", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼聲音？", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糟糕，他還是按下了計時器......", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#3$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有不到一分鐘了——", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_explosion_stone"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g11_monitoringroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那C1、C2還回得來嗎......", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會親自向長官們申請，為他們，以及今天殉職的所有戰友，發放軍功章。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上校，那可是，一整個副總統車隊——五輛車，十多個隨行人員，萬一附近還有萊茵職員和記者、行人......", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "服從命令，雷克。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由我來親自按下遙控裝置，這是我站在這裡的任務......而你的任務，是在C1、C2的爆破訊號傳來的時候，第一時間向我匯報。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "未來我可能會站在軍事法庭上，接受程序或道德的審判，我不會為自己辯解。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以此時此刻，我不想浪費口舌向我的士兵解釋什麼。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是。", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "訊號來了！", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "副總統的車隊也即將行駛到萊茵生命西側的指定區域。", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上校？", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布萊克的手放在了那枚冰冷的機械按鈕上，涼意瞬間爬上他的手指，他停頓了兩秒。"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "士兵瞥了一眼自己的長官，墨鏡後他的眉毛皺得很緊。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "士兵突然反應過來，其實他比自己還緊張......"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低聲）*哥倫比亞粗口*！", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#7$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.3}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_button"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布萊克按下了按鈕。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有聲音，只有部分監視螢幕上出現了爆炸的畫面。"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那些微縮的視界裡，頃刻間淪陷的街道像是保麗龍，火光只是泛白的圖像。所有的畫面突然消失，大概是攝影機被擊飛的磚石摧毀了。"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有聲音，但布萊克和士兵似乎都聽見了爆炸聲，震耳欲聾。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個方向，應該快到地面了才對，但這些石板把路全封住了，看不見......", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#9$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你們倆沒事吧？", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#3$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糟糕，是連環爆炸。", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#4$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊芙利特？！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#4$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個無比熟悉的聲音穿透爆炸的餘波和土石墜落的窸窣動靜，鑽進了伊芙利特的耳朵。"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞雷婭？我在這裡！", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#6$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽到了......堅持住！", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#6$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鎖定你的位置了！", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#6$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_surfacefrozen"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊芙利特清楚地聽出了塞雷婭的聲音在輕微顫抖，黑暗中，有什麼東西觸碰到了她的手指......鈣質結晶？那是塞雷婭的源石技藝。"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鈣質結晶像是穩定的水流，沿著土石的縫隙迅速連成一片，再猛然撐開，周圍的結構因為擠壓而發出令人牙酸的異響——"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞雷婭強行在坍塌的地下結構中開出了一條狹窄的甬道。"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隻手伸了下來，伊芙利特跳起握住，一股強大的力量將自己拽向地面，鈣質甬道在身後轟然碎裂。"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-80", "duration": 0.1, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g8_alley_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,-80", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#6$1", "posfrom": "-50,-150", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別動。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#3$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒事，只是碰了點灰而已。", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#6$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的臉......你剛才哭過了嗎？", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#4$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我才沒有哭！只是有點著急了而已！", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#3$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞雷婭，你的手上也都是灰，越擦我臉上越髒了！", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#7$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......啊，抱歉。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#3$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩個人？", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是他們兩個在地下結構放炸藥，炸了液化源石氣的管道，所以我把他們帶了出來。", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是塞雷婭，我沒能阻止爆炸......", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#6$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經做得很好了。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#7$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......真的。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#5$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊芙利特，你在看什麼？", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#8$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#5$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_895_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默？你怎麼來了？", "name": "伊芙利特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#5$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......赫默。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#5$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼，你們會在這裡？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_895_1#5$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g7_mainstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "副總統先生，帕瓦爾秘書，現在可以上車了。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛那個車隊？", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#3$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請放心，只是炸毀了一些機甲而已。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這輛私家車經過了工程科的改裝，不起眼，但可以放心。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麻煩帕瓦爾秘書充當一下司機，走萊茵生命大樓東側的特別通道離開，我們已經規劃好了新的路線。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的其他隨行人員，則會在事情結束後分批返回。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛的爆炸，也在你們的預料之中？", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並沒有。這種規模的爆炸，如果事先得到了情報，我們肯定會予以排除。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是在副總統先生回到住所之前，萊茵生命和梅蘭德基金會的工作都還沒有結束罷了......對方不止一項計劃，我們自然也不止一套預案。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#5$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，我不希望明天的新聞上出現“第二個特萊頓工廠”之類的字眼。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記者那邊，我們已經有了安排，請您放心。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再一次祝您在特里蒙接下來的旅程順利。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drivestop"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Image", "